Detailed Description

cvmx_sso_pp::_qos_pri

CSR reserved addresses: (56): 0x2040..0x21f8 CSR align addresses: =========================================================================================================== SSO_PP(0..31)_QOS_PRI = SSO PP QOS Priority Register (one field per IQ per PP)

Contains the QOS level priorities for each PP. 0x0 is the highest priority 0x7 is the lowest priority 0xf prevents the PP from receiving work from that QOS level 0x8-0xe Reserved

For a given PP, priorities should begin at 0x0, and remain contiguous throughout the range. Failure to do so may result in severe performance degradation.

Priorities for IQs 0..7
